What are we trying to accomplish?

flowRoot.flowPara: Choosing a cartridge gear size is simple: the gear size select box is populated with gear sizes the user has access to.
A help popup contains resource information for the various gear sizes.
When only a single size is available, the select box is replaced with just the gear profile name.
This should not appear at all in a non-scalable application.
